        <abstract> 
<p>Though not sanguine about sale [of <hi rend="italic">Erasmus Darwin</hi>] it seems fair that if over 1500 copies are sold he should receive two-thirds profit. If JM does not agree, he would prefer publishing on commission or asking Macmillan if they will give him larger profits.</p> 
